data.name: NON-WOVEN FIX TAPE
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% Nonwoven Flexible fabric
- Medical Paper
- Adhesive: Acrylic and Hotmelt

## STERILIZATION
- Non-Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Straight and Curved Cut Transfer Paper
- Various Shapes
- With and without Haemostatic Island

## PERFORMANCE
- Highly Flexible
- Skin friendly
- Aseptic, non-sterile
- Hypoallergenic
- Strong hold without skin irritation (Latex-free)
